# Research standards

Source priority: official venue/company pages → government/transit → universities →
annual reports → statistical agencies → OECD/academic → reputable local press →
community (subjective texture only).

Every volatile claim needs a Claim record with sourceIds, accessed/verified dates,
confidence, and reverifyAfter.

Distinguish traveler-provided, researched, inferred, and confirmed.
